{
  "texts": [
    "ADAM is used as the optimiser (as implemented in torch).Nested.",
    "To ensure fair comparisons, the nested comparisons are run with the same hyperparamaters as the proposed.",
    "However, follower (resp.",
    "leader) specific parameters are decayed at a rate based only on the number of follower (resp.",
    "leader) updates.All approaches are run on a CPU, with Python3, and on an Amazon EC2 with R6i.large."
  ]
}